"04/30/2020 06:16am","148.71.8.245","0","+351938218974","lifesgrand1967@gmail.com","12/March/1967","En couple","Intendant Général - Régisseur - House manager","1607 PA","Maria Alexandra Almeida - I have had many jobs in my carreer.  After graduating from high school I have worked as a sales representative for a pharmaceutical lab, in Lisbon. I then moved abroad and worked as a Personal Assistant for the M&A director of a private bank in New York, and after that as a PA to the EMEA manager of a computer company in the UK.  Upon returning to Portugal I have worked as the manager of the Flexjet program for a private jet company, in Lisbon and also as a PR and F&B manager at a small restaurant in Lisbon.  For the past 16 years I worked as the housekeeper of a well-known Portuguese politician who unfortunately died and thus the reason for me to be looking for a position.  In this household I was responsible for managing the permanent staff of six and making sure everything was properly done and maintained.  I know how to do everything as i believe it is impossible to tell others what must be done if you do not know how to do it yourself properly.  In this last employment my boss entertained on a daily basis and he was extremely attentive to detail.  Not only the interior of the house but also the garden and the pool area had to be in perfect conditions at all times.  Because cooking was one of his passions it was the boss who told the kitchen staff what was to be prepared but it was my job to make sure all ingredients were fresh and cooked properly, as per his request.  I also helped the boss with his own private correspondence, payments of staff salaries, insurances, maintenance of the car fleet, organization of international business trips and also vacation trips with his family.  I always accompannied them on these vacation trips as his daughters have children and I would usually babbysit for them during the night when they would go out for diners.  I also did babysitting for his grandchildren at other times when the nannies were busy with other chores.  I love babies and children and have an excellent rapport with them.  Taking care of the four house pets was another of my responsibilities whenever the dog sitter was not available.  Overall it was an experience I will always cherish.  I am healthy and in excellent physical shape as I do not smoke and exercise regularly.

Mateus Rosa - Other than the professional experience you can see in my resume, in my free time I have also done a multitude of other part-time jobs such as personal trainer, driver and body guard whilst in Florianopolis, Brazil.  In Portugal I have further increased my former professional experience in all the subjects have referenced in my resumé and also I had the opportunity of working as an assistant cook which is something that I truly love and am quite good at.  I am a very good worker and do not have any problem with working hours.  I am strong and very fit.
