Je reste à votre disposition pour toute information complémentaire et pour vous rencontrer lors d’un entretien.


Veuillez agréer, Madame, Monsieur, l’expression de mes sincères salutations.","<a href='http://www.weebly.com/editor/uploads/9/9/9/5/9995793/744395834808482338_margaux_berlan_1.pdf' target='_blank'>margaux_berlan_1.pdf</a>","<a href='http://www.weebly.com/editor/uploads/9/9/9/5/9995793/653073833606927290_capture_decran_2020-05-11_a_12.21.21.png' target='_blank'>capture_decran_2020-05-11_a_12.21.21.png</a>","","J'accepte les conditions générales*","Margaux Berlan","Une Femme","35 avenue des vignerons","","Un homme",""
"05/11/2020 04:34am","77.134.167.55","0","0618782678","anaisvasseur06@gmail.com","18/04/1994","Célibataire","Assistant personnel","1567 PA","Objet: Assistante trilingue

