Most notably, in my recent position as International Sales and Customer Service employee, I was responsible to maintain customer database, give advice/support to new and existing customers, update price-lists and draft offers, process orders, issue invoices and shipping documents, monitor and coordinate on delivery and payment status, participate in trade fairs, establish contact with potential customers and provide follow-up, ensure administrative and organizational support. In addition to that, I collaborate with Turkish trade fair projects in Italy and provide support for organizational and liaison issues. 

After having lived in Milan for the last 4 years, I would like to explore new employment opportunities that means that I am available for relocation. I strongly believe that my combination of competences developed through professional experience as described above, together with my language skills (I speak English, French, Turkish, Russian, Italian, Georgian and I am at intermediate level in my German studies) and liaison abilities in a multicultural environment will enable me to assume the responsibilities defined for the subject position.

