"05/25/2020 06:29am","85.170.195.80","0","+447961398935","ZackTurley1993@hotmail.co.uk","16/12/1993","Célibataire","Chef Cuisinier","1592 PA","I am a chef who learned his craft in the United Kingdom at the age of 19. I have been learning and perfecting my craft throughout my 20s working in various fine dining restaurants and gastro pubs. I have had the opportunity to learn and study different cuisines along my way helping my overall understanding of cooking. 

I decided to furthermore challenge myself by moving to Sydney, Australia to help extend my knowledge in a different country where i became Sous chef of a mediterranean fine dinning restaurant within my first week. 

I have most experience in seafood dishes due to working primarily in seafood restaurants whilst i was younger. However, I am more than capable and confident of working in every area of a kitchen from meat to pastry. 

I have been working as a sous chef for the past two years so have the understanding and management skills to be able to work efficiently on my own and lead a team. I've also learned to be creative and to produce my own dishes and to keep within the allocated budget. 

I have learned to adapt and have become very flexible to be able to suit the clients needs. I can produce a high quality and nutritious dishes that can hold up to my high expectations. My attention to detail is important to me and i want that to reflect in the food i produce,","<a href='http://www.weebly.com/editor/uploads/9/9/9/5/9995793/530714197317186762_zack_turley_french_cv.docx' target='_blank'>zack_turley_french_cv.docx</a>","<a href='http://www.weebly.com/editor/uploads/9/9/9/5/9995793/586751713286729512_img_3335.jpg' target='_blank'>img_3335.jpg</a>","","J'accepte les conditions générales*","Zack Turley","Un homme","8 RUE PETEL 75015 PARIS","","Un homme",""
"05/25/2020 07:21am","37.165.28.184","0","0782695323","nathalie_bartholet@hotmail.com","19/09/1962","En couple","Couple de Gardien","candidature spontanée","Bonjour,

