Je vous prie d’agréer Madame mais salutations distinguées.
Nicolas Lemaire","","<a href='http://www.weebly.com/editor/uploads/9/9/9/5/9995793/803938379118309244_82b4b4fa-554c-46fa-ade9-5048507fb0a5.jpeg' target='_blank'>82b4b4fa-554c-46fa-ade9-5048507fb0a5.jpeg</a>","","J'accepte les conditions générales*","Lemaire Nicolas ","Un homme","29  rue du Maréchal foch 
