"06/08/2020 01:28pm","37.117.54.130","0","+393473330175","Info@lucarobledo.com ","27-01-1982 ","Marié","Chef Cuisinier","1692 PA","To whom it may concern

Dear Sirs,


My name is Luca Robledo, I'm an Italian Private – Personal Chef from Italy.


I have been working in the industry in senior positions for eight years, first as Head Chef in restaurants, hotels and fairs, and afterwards as a Private Chef for single clients.


For the latter business, I have developed different exclusive packages: live-in service from breakfast to dinner for short terms commitments (from one week to two months), dinner events, cooking shows and cooking classes, catering service for parties, gala dinners.



I am based on Como Lake, Northern of Italy, but for live-in services I am happy to travel worldwide, if required.


My mission is to take care of my clients as far as all their needs about food and its service are concerned. I have shifted towards servicing private customers as I strongly believe that a personalised service can make the difference in today's commercial offers.



Attention to details can only be achieved and offered in private settings. This is why when I am on duty, I do not take days off nor have scheduled working times: I’m available for my clients 24/7 for the entire time of their stay / holiday / travel. 


My cuisine is based on the Italian tradition, which is already pretty diverse. However, I experiment contaminations and can prepare Asian and Middle Eastern courses too. Needless to say, I cook vegan and vegetarian meals and take extreme care of any intolerance and allergy.



I also guarantee the organic quality, seasonality, and local sourcing of my food. I am environment-conscious and carry out a nearly total no-waste cooking policy.


My usual rate is €250/day (grocery purchase excluded), but I am open to negotiate lump fees for longer engagements.


I currently do not have the CRB check, but I can provide asap should you require me to do so.

Also, I am happy to provide written references from some of my top clients upon request.


I look forward to hearing from you soon.

With very best regards","<a href='http://www.weebly.com/editor/uploads/9/9/9/5/9995793/734409474508890101_cv_luca_robledo_eng.pdf' target='_blank'>cv_luca_robledo_eng.pdf</a>","","","J'accepte les conditions générales*","Luca Robledo ","Un homme","Via brambilla 13, Como, Italie ","","Un homme",""
